{"tid":614922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：將去函港大促暫停戴耀廷教學工作　「多行不義必自斃」","createTime":"2018-04-03T03:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T04:56:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"08ad69f13682b7cd7e744963bd95b20e0698d921","tid":614922,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/benny-01_eNAsj_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbenny-01_eNAsj_1200x0.png&h=8dce1090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港大法律系副教授戴耀廷早前在台灣出席論壇，提到在大陸成為一個民主的國家後，港人可考慮是否成立獨立國家，被特區政府、中聯辦、港澳辦、建制派等先後發聲明譴責。立法會議員何君堯今日在《文匯報》撰文，稱自己將「不忘初心」，繼續強烈要求港大革走戴耀廷，以免他在大學荼毒學生。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯去年曾發起「反港獨、反冷血、反偽學」集會，批評戴耀廷策動佔領中環是「港獨」思潮的罪魁禍首，要求港大辭退戴耀廷。本身是律師的何稱，戴耀廷在台灣發表的言論更不是在推動民主，而是徹徹底底鼓吹「港獨」，公然分裂國家，煽動港人參與其中，已屬違法行為，絕對不能置之不理。<br />\n<br />\n何又稱將會去函港大要求正視此事，促使校方成立委員會調查戴耀廷在校內外的言行，以及是否仍適合任教，期間校方須暫停戴耀廷的教學工作，「以免戴在校園裡繼續宣揚『港獨』、『自決』等違法言論，誤導學生，希望校方能明確作出回應。」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯去又指出，革走戴耀廷是廣大市民的共同期待，港大校方不應也不能置之不理，不能縱容包庇，基本法第23條立法是特區政府的憲制責任，對於戴耀廷等應立刻依法檢控，同時盡快展開基本法第23條立法的工作，「在此，我奉勸戴耀廷，多行不義必自斃。若想得到救贖，必須立刻停止一切狡辯和抵賴，真誠承認自己的錯誤，勇於接受鼓吹煽動『港獨』的後果，立即辭去港大教職，停止荼毒學生。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/何君堯-將去函港大促暫停戴耀廷教學工作-多行不義必自斃/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%B0%87%E5%8E%BB%E5%87%BD%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%83%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8D%E7%BE%A9%E5%BF%85%E8%87%AA%E6%96%83%2F&d=sQ1Ss9FfJaHbKDeFcVq3fozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=f068b002\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E5%B0%87%E5%8E%BB%E5%87%BD%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%83%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%8D%E7%BE%A9%E5%BF%85%E8%87%AA%E6%96%83%2F&h=32edda6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/何君堯-將去函港大促暫停戴耀廷教學工作-多行不義必自斃/</a>"},{"pid":"a47c5e16a40e80a37d6f2576eec9687f42b87b15","tid":614922,"uid":40470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:16:23.000Z","msg":"話自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ef5845e59cab71594268c83494fd57180cf01d","tid":614922,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"同緊自己講<br />\n<br />\n定係同民主建國聯盟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21ae30e34217e002c474e3d8ba0f79d87f57907","tid":614922,"uid":18167,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/ho-27_raB0f_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fho-27_raB0f_1200x0.png&h=41a7a48d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"744c95cb8903e658db9d4ce8e617a9b83762fca9","tid":614922,"uid":1874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:18:23.000Z","msg":"屌佢自己行左咁多不義都未死啦"},{"pid":"89cdb3208070da072f9d4182f3e05a10f1654f46","tid":614922,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/111853_67e3d42f73b9851f93645367978cc5d1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F111853_67e3d42f73b9851f93645367978cc5d1.png&h=791e2e9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e25d8515282d0e83b525e406ff25e4a8507f75e","tid":614922,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:20:10.000Z","msg":"你自己咪生勾勾"},{"pid":"4701b049fed036f66377928f75ce6802006ce6e4","tid":614922,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"744c95cb8903e65